  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Edward Morris Davis has delayed in sending Maria Weston Chapman the enclosed letter from Lucretia Mott in the hopes of having a proper inspiration for a contribution to the Liberty Bell.</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">In the postscript, Edward Morris Davis says that he is anxiously waiting for the plan by which he can learn French verbs without effort. Also, he declares himself the happiest man living because he has another little boy.</subfield>
